c: 7
v: 20
t: "Tokkel sheytan ken nammay Yalli ken kak waase caxah mexexu yakmeenimkeh waswasa keenil yekke, ken nammayih Qawratak keenik Qellittem ken yaybulleemkeh, sin Rabbi tama caxak sin kah waasem mali isin namma Malaykattu takkeenimik hinnay jannatal waara marih loowot gace waytaanamkeh iyyaanam akke waytek keenik iyye"